{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4590fddc42","title":"致郭洪涛电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d922d76925","index":0,"year":1938,"month":9,"day":7,"articleId":"4590fddc42"}],"tags":[{"id":"1f0832775e","name":"王明","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji12.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji12":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fce24f48a2","type":"paragraph","text":"致郭洪涛电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"4590fddc42"},{"id":"a8fbd2750c","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年9月7日）郭洪涛同志山东各党派军队与我们的关系进一步好转，已使我们有可能开始在黄河以东建立大块抗日根据地。望你们根据我党抗日教国十大纲领及政后战区工作的基本原则与山东的实际情况，和石友三议定共同建立山东抗日根据地的纲领。建立根据地的各方面工作可由石友三公开出面来做","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"4590fddc42"},{"id":"d7cb48377f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛洛胡","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"4590fddc42"},{"id":"f856a382f0","type":"paragraph","text":"七日1这是毛泽东和洛甫（张同天）、胡服（刘少奇）给郭洪毒的电报。1938年9月，毛泽东、朱德等到机场迎接从武汉回延安参加六届六中全会的王明、周恩来、秦邦宪、徐特立等1938年9月，延安各界为王明、周恩来、秦邦宪、徐特立从武汉回到延安举行欢迎大会，毛泽东出席会议。前排右二为毛泽东。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"4590fddc42"}],"page":{"id":"353cdcdfb6","publicationId":"maoquanji12","articleId":"4590fddc42","start":437,"end":438}}}},"__N_SSG":true}